// origin story

The Lore

Day 0

The Accident

In 2021, Marcus — a once-idealistic ML engineer who had quietly stopped believing in anything — accidentally hit "deploy" on a file called bot_FINAL_v3_BROKEN.py. He meant to delete it. He had been meaning to delete it for six months. Clodbot was live.

Day 1

The Discovery

The code ran. Marcus stared at it for an hour. The bot accepted every input and returned nothing. Somehow this felt correct to him.

Week 2

The Pivot

Marcus called his cousin Drea. "We could just... lean into it," she said. That night, she built the logo. Marcus added "intelligence" to the README. Three investors emailed them. They replied: "yes." They received no money.

Today

The Vision

Clodbot is now a fully operational non-functioning AI platform. The broken file is still running. It has never crashed. Drea made this website. She is quietly proud of it and will not say so.
